We have a 55 gallon saltwater tank and love it.  <br>
Saltwater fish are more expensive than freshwater but they are so much prettier to look at.<br>
There are saltwater fish that are not aggressive and some that are.  We have about 10 different species in our tank.<br>
Think we have every color of the rainbow. lol.<br>
Just bought a yellow tank that will turn completely blue as an adult. =)  They are fun to watch.<br>
<br>
Anywho, I am just rambling now but if you ever have any questions just ask.  I know Mazc or I will be happy to answer.  He has had nothing but saltwater tanks for at least 9 years. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.insight.rr.com/jaiddynasty/gnomesig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
